#: templates/terms_of_service.html:37
msgid ""
"We strive to maintain high availability but do not guarantee uninterrupted "
"service. We may perform maintenance that temporarily affects availability."
msgstr ""
"Биз сервистин жогорку жеткиликтүүлүгүн сактоого аракет кылабыз, бирок "
